<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - SRC Travel Agencies</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-icons/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-800 font-sans">
    <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-r class bg-blue-900 text-white py-24 px-6 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto z-10 relative">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight">SRC Travel Agencies</h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-blue-200 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Connecting destinations, elevating journeys. We are proud to be the nation's leading private transport enterprise.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-950 opacity-40 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-16 px-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-6 relative after:content-[''] after:block after:w-16 after:h-1 after:bg-blue-600 after:mt-2">
                    Our Story
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                    Established with a vision to redefine inter-provincial travel, <strong>SRC Travel Agencies</strong> has grown from a regional operator into a nationwide transportation network. We bridge distances, linking central branches with distant provinces to ensure seamless transit for thousands of passengers daily.
                </p>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                    By transitioning from traditional, counter-based ledger booking to an advanced, real-time centralized management ecosystem, we continuously optimize our operational flows to put passenger comfort and security first.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl h-80 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-900 shadow-inner relative overflow-hidden">
                <span class="font-semibold text-lg z-10">SRC Nationwide Fleet</span>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600/10 to-blue-900/20"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="bg-white py-16 px-6 border-y border-slate-200">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-3">Our Premium Fleet</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-500">Tailored comfort for every passenger on every route</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow bg-slate-50">
                    <div class="text-blue-600 text-3xl mb-4"><i class="fas fa-bus"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Express Class</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Our standard, highly cost-effective option available in both Air-Conditioned (A/C) and Non-A/C variants. Perfect for regular inter-city commuters.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow bg-slate-50">
                    <div class="text-blue-600 text-3xl mb-4"><i class="fas fa-couch"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Luxury Class</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        An upgraded travel experience featuring enhanced seating ergonomics, climate control, and additional amenities to make mid-distance trips refreshing.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="border border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow bg-blue-50/50 relative">
                    <span class="absolute -top-3 right-4 bg-blue-600 text-white text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full font-semibold">Flagship</span>
                    <div class="text-blue-600 text-3xl mb-4"><i class="fas fa-crown"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Volvo Flagship</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        The ultimate luxury. Our top-tier premium coaches equipped with advanced suspension, spacious berths, and top-of-the-line real-time seat synchronization tracking.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-16 px-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-3">Core Commitments</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500">Driven by technology, structured for reliability</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <div class="p-5 text-center">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 mx-auto mb-4 text-xl"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i></div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Real-time Booking</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Instantly update and synchronize seat availability across all ticket counters.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 text-center">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 mx-auto mb-4 text-xl"><i class="fas fa-calculator"></i></div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Fair Pricing Rules</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Automated fare structures dynamically calculated by age, distance, and vehicle tier.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 text-center">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 mx-auto mb-4 text-xl"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i></div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Centralized Security</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Strict role-based management ensuring that operational data is fully guarded.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 text-center">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 mx-auto mb-4 text-xl"><i class="fas fa-users"></i></div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Inclusive Care</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs">Dedicated discount policies to guarantee accessible transit for all age groups.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-400 py-8 text-center text-sm border-t border-slate-800">
        <p>&copy; 2026 SRC Travel Agencies. Integrated Central System. Developed by Team Code Tích Cực.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>